<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als uns ewr gnade
                                    <add><expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan></add>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        Schafstet genant Prewss und auch von Görgen <expan>Ehalt<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        des Hutkapfers bruder, etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und lassen ewr gnade
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und kawfflewt, die die sache antrift, zu
                                <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> niht anheim sint, daz wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> niht <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>
<expan>künne<ex>n</ex></expan>. Denn als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> nehst <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>gebett<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz ir <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        davor sein wolt, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> veynd, die uns doch
                                <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> recht
                            <expan>angreiff<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>beschedig<ex>en</ex></expan>, in <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sloss<ex>en</ex></expan> iht mer <expan>gehalt<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> und in aus <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>sloss<ex>en</ex></expan> und von den <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> iht
                        hilff oder zuschüb beschehen, also <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                        gnade <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> ir wellet das also
                                <expan>bestell<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir umb ewr gnade allczeit
                                <expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und gern
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>s<ex>upra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
